  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model predicts absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. All 13 credibility factors were assessed under the ASME V&V 40-2018 framework for the intended use scope of pre-clinical regulatory submission supporting a Class III implantable VAD. Decision: Accepted with documented rationale.",
